name: FOSS-Xtensa
tagline: Free OpenSource Software for the Xtensa processor architecture
body:
The repositories hosted on GitHub are used for development (feeding into the respective mainline repositories), projects that haven't yet added support for the Xtensa architecture, and other useful projects.

For more information, please see also the [Wiki](http://wiki.linux-xtensa.org).
